title: Marin_Note_Cleanse
tags: examine note mission2
---
// Re-examined in Mission 2 — now reveals a second paragraph.
NotePinned: Polish in slow circles. The faster you press, the less the orb hears you.
NotePinned: Cover all sides. Most memories need ninety seconds.
NotePinned: To Cleanse: find the cracks. Trace them once, fully, without lifting your hand.
NotePinned: Never touch the warm center. The warm center is the memory itself.
NotePinned: If you touch it, you have not cleansed; you have erased.
NotePinned: — M.

===

